Doubles the research EXP gained
after sleep research. Good for one
sleep session, then consumed.
item_desc_10:
A nice treat that will make a Pokémon
quite a bit more friendly toward you.
This biscuit gives three friendship
points.
item_desc_11:
A special treat that will make a
Pokémon as friendly as can be. This
biscuit maxes out friendship points.

species of Pokémon.

of Pokémon.

can be turned into 100 candies for
any species of Pokémon.

A string exuding a mysterious energy
that makes you feel a strange sense
of connection.
item_desc_22:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It has a fiery orange heart.
item_desc_23:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It is the clear blue of a deep pool.
item_desc_24:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It has a distinct thunderbolt pattern.
item_desc_25:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It has an unmistakable leaf pattern.
item_desc_26:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It has a snowflake pattern in it.
item_desc_27:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It is dark like the night sky.
item_desc_28:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It shines with a dazzling light.
item_desc_29:
A metallic coating that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It is made of a special metal.
item_desc_3:
Doubles the EXP that helpers gain
after sleep research. Good for one
sleep session, then consumed.
item_desc_30:
A peculiar stone that can make a
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It is round and smooth.
item_desc_31:
A peculiar stone that can make
certain species of Pokémon evolve.
It is shaped like a crown.
item_desc_32:
A mysterious seed that can raise the
level of a Pokémon's main skill by one.
item_desc_33:
A mysterious seed that can improve
the quality of a Pokémon’s random
sub skill by one.
item_desc_34:
Ensures that at least one Pokémon
will appear during snack time feeling
particularly hungry. Good for one
sleep session, then consumed.
item_desc_4:
Doubles the Energy that helpers
recover after sleep research. Good
for one sleep session, then consumed.
item_desc_5:
A specially made pillow that restores
50 Energy to a single helper Pokémon.
item_desc_6:
An especially energizing whistle.
One blow, and your team of helpers
will gather 3 hours' worth of Berries
and ingredients for you. This will not
cause main skills to trigger.
item_desc_7:
A special ticket that lets you move
to another site at any time.
(You can only move to areas you have
already unlocked)
item_desc_8:
Lets you borrow a Good Camp Set
for seven days to aid your research
and help you raise Snorlax.
item_desc_9:
A treat that will make a Pokémon a
little more friendly toward you. This
biscuit gives one friendship point.
